<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>8753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今晚我们玩儿游戏吧！”朱迪姑姑说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好啊！”艾米和哈利大声回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一开始，大家玩儿的是棋盘游戏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾米抛了色子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47558</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她走了五步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后轮到哈利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56974</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以走六步！”哈利说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都轮流了几次。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快艾米的棋子走在了最前面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾米又扔了一次色子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀！”艾米说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得退后三步。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着哈利走了十二步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的棋子最先到达了目的地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我赢了！”哈利说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是最棒的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾米皱了皱眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈利，要有点儿风度！”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗也皱了皱眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也想赢！”奥利弗抱怨道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奥利弗，要有点儿风度！”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149043</EndMilliseconds>
