  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>朱迪姑姑摇了摇头，什么都没有说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是一只海豹吗？”艾米问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181462</EndMilliseconds>
